-[#484848]/30">"ai"</code>) with an associated probability score. The model=
 outputs logits over 2-3 classes depending on whether the model was trained=
 with a "mixed" category.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Detection Mode</strong>: Produces character-level intervals mark=
ing AI-generated spans within the text. The DETR architecture generates 45 =
object queries, each predicting interval boundaries (start and end characte=
r positions). Post-processing applies confidence thresholding and merges ov=
erlapping intervals.</p>
</li>
</ul>
