<ol>
<li><strong>Tokenization</strong>: Converts input text to token IDs using t=
he Mistral tokenizer</li>
<li><strong>Forward Pass</strong>: Runs the tokenized input through the mod=
el to obtain logits</li>
<li><strong>Probability Calculation</strong>: Applies softmax to logits to =
get probability distribution over classes</li>
<li><strong>Label Assignment</strong>: Selects the class with highest proba=
bility</li>
</ol>
