<ol>
<li><strong>Tokenization</strong>: Converts input text to token IDs</li>
<li><strong>Forward Pass</strong>: DETR model predicts 45 interval candidat=
es with confidence scores</li>
<li><strong>Confidence Filtering</strong>: Removes predictions below confid=
ence threshold</li>
<li><strong>Interval Merging</strong>: Combines overlapping or adjacent int=
ervals</li>
<li><strong>Character Mapping</strong>: Maps token positions back to charac=
ter indices in original text</li>
</ol>
<p>The detection mode preserves character-level precision by maintaining a =
mapping between tokenized positions and original character positions throug=
hout the pipeline.</p>
